{"tid":1137410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[女權x素食] 妮妲莉寶雯: 吃蛋和奶是對女性身體的剝削 [嚇撚死你]","createTime":"2019-05-03T17:42:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T03:08:05.000Z","uid":119393,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"89290982664e85212ec2a55f2db16047789a4c0f","tid":1137410,"uid":119393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T17:42:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://health.udn.com/health/story/5999/3788655\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhealth.udn.com%2Fhealth%2Fstory%2F5999%2F3788655&d=piXtWL8Gd%2FER6BG70pbW90YD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=d2e3366a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://health.udn.com/health/story/5999/3788655</a><br />\n<br />\n美國知名演員娜塔莉&middot;波曼（Natalie Portman）先前在一個公開場合，對大眾呼籲吃純素，還稱奶和蛋是對「女（雌）性動物的剝削」，引發部分網友熱議和質疑。<br />\n<br />\n外媒報導，娜塔莉波曼日前在洛杉磯的We Day論壇上，對上萬名學生宣揚純素食主義，她表示牛奶和雞蛋不僅是來自牛和雞，更是來自母牛和母雞，這代表我們正在剝削女性的身體，濫用雌性動物的魔力來製造牛奶和雞蛋。<br />\n<br />\n娜塔莉波曼指出，她活躍於女性相關話題後，才意識到素食主義和這話題密切相關。為了製造牛奶，母親和孩子被迫分離，動物生活在如監獄般擁擠且多病的環境，製造乳製品和蛋類。<br />\n<br />\n波曼說很多人嘲笑素食主義者，嘲笑關心任何事情的人，但她呼籲按照自己的信念去吃，關心這件事永遠是好的，敞開心扉、把別人的痛苦當作自己的痛苦去關心和改變，就是最美好的事。<br />\n<br />\n娜塔莉波曼9歲起就成為素食主義者，並在8年前成為純素主義者，她稱會這麼做是把動物當作孩童，而且這樣對地球有利。為了她愛護動物、力推環保的立場，戲服設計師還曾特別應她要求，以不傷害動物的標準來製作所有戲服。"},{"pid":"5fa3a4bf450d9b840d257e2bff435ab5b4951cb7","tid":1137410,"uid":48579,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T17:45:12.000Z","msg":"終極煩膠混合體 素食女權環保者"},{"pid":"1fe64cb8b42179b9437a16b3d11de803eaaaf6e7","tid":1137410,"uid":49197,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T17:51:40.000Z","msg":"Natalie Portman係啱ge,佢叫我幫佢奶閪都制"},{"pid":"3d5d1b5023120c3b7be0e65483ce0d4af113aa08","tid":1137410,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T18:35:35.000Z","msg":"聽講佢讀好撚多書？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c29695247152479c43cf7657ea08e85750446cb","tid":1137410,"uid":233557,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T18:38:52.000Z","msg":"大概係佢本身就唔鍾意食肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee30f5117326697a78e54f895f6f488478f453e","tid":1137410,"uid":29942,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T18:39:33.000Z","msg":"剝削植物就得呀？"},{"pid":"b32cfa1a494ba9e7ab73a3ee8350fde1e9d7ecc7","tid":1137410,"uid":23104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T18:41:51.000Z","msg":"早幾日有人開左post啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1132125\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1132125</a>"},{"pid":"cd04000064b317731b861c678aea7fe8162e8395","tid":1137410,"uid":190431,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"5fa3a4bf450d9b840d257e2bff435ab5b4951cb7","tid":1137410,"uid":48579,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T17:45:12.000Z","msg":"終極煩膠混合體 素食女權環保者"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T18:42:03.000Z","msg":"口不對心，咁佢又拍chanel香水廣告？無人話佢知香水都係用動物腺體製造。"},{"pid":"8fab53baeaf1e35967ab5a226d5a40a7cbc006a2","tid":1137410,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cd04000064b317731b861c678aea7fe8162e8395","tid":1137410,"uid":190431,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"5fa3a4bf450d9b840d257e2bff435ab5b4951cb7","tid":1137410,"uid":48579,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T17:45:12.000Z","msg":"終極煩膠混合體 素食女權環保者"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T18:42:03.000Z","msg":"口不對心，咁佢又拍chanel香水廣告？無人話佢知香水都係用動物腺體製造。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T18:43:09.000Z","msg":"噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590a4f394d9c761cf4e3d4a12ad42b4b7d0d354d","tid":1137410,"uid":162095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T18:47:27.000Z","msg":"差在唔係耶撚"},{"pid":"b575d816fc4844936ce9532a59bf4272f707b65e","tid":1137410,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T20:29:31.000Z","msg":"X永遠係Y前面<br />\n<br />\n是對Y的侮辱"},{"pid":"271aba4303917cbe66